    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Brain Kosmos"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"fdc06e94-0c21-5a0e-b0e8-ba5db9630683","excerpt":"There are many ways to display content on a screen, and depending on which device you use, it can affect how good it looks. On devices in landscape mode, the…","html":"<p>There are many ways to display content on a screen, and depending on which device you use, it can affect how good it looks. On devices in landscape mode, the width offers extra real estate for your content, but not without cost. Extra width does not mean extra line length, as it would be rather difficult to read the next line by darting your eyes from one end of the screen to the other. <sup id=\"fnref-1\"><a href=\"#fn-1\" class=\"footnote-ref\">1</a></sup></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eb737e44895b70ed06937af4c85bfca8/df88b/lorem-ipsum-long-width.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 6.329113924050632%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAQUlEQVQI1zXGyw2AIBAAUYsxIgsm7AdORvuvaoxED5M3i3rw59FR8/n2vgfNHPuMPmhq7FLIpSL1IGWZrlvivG4e5vkfTllkNp8AAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Lorem Ipsum Long Width\"\n        title=\"Lorem Ipsum Long Width\"\n        src=\"/static/eb737e44895b70ed06937af4c85bfca8/f058b/lorem-ipsum-long-width.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eb737e44895b70ed06937af4c85bfca8/c26ae/lorem-ipsum-long-width.png 158w,\n/static/eb737e44895b70ed06937af4c85bfca8/6bdcf/lorem-ipsum-long-width.png 315w,\n/static/eb737e44895b70ed06937af4c85bfca8/f058b/lorem-ipsum-long-width.png 630w,\n/static/eb737e44895b70ed06937af4c85bfca8/40601/lorem-ipsum-long-width.png 945w,\n/static/eb737e44895b70ed06937af4c85bfca8/78612/lorem-ipsum-long-width.png 1260w,\n/static/eb737e44895b70ed06937af4c85bfca8/df88b/lorem-ipsum-long-width.png 1906w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Instead, we can make use of the extra space while keeping it at a readable width by sectioning content into columns using CSS Grid.</p>\n<h2>Split Content into Columns</h2>\n<p>Let’s solve the problem that was shown in the example above. We’ll display the texts in 3 columns of equal width on a single row.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. A pellentesque sit amet porttitor. Non enim praesent elementum facilisis. Nunc aliquet bibendum enim facilisis gravida neque convallis a. Vitae aliquet nec ullamcorper sit amet risus nullam. Porttitor lacus luctus accumsan tortor posuere ac ut consequat semper. Pulvinar etiam non quam lacus suspendisse. Cursus risus at ultrices mi tempus imperdiet nulla malesuada pellentesque. Morbi enim nunc faucibus a pellentesque sit. Gravida dictum fusce ut placerat orci nulla pellentesque dignissim.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. A pellentesque sit amet porttitor. Non enim praesent elementum facilisis. Nunc aliquet bibendum enim facilisis gravida neque convallis a. Vitae aliquet nec ullamcorper sit amet risus nullam. Porttitor lacus luctus accumsan tortor posuere ac ut consequat semper. Pulvinar etiam non quam lacus suspendisse. Cursus risus at ultrices mi tempus imperdiet nulla malesuada pellentesque. Morbi enim nunc faucibus a pellentesque sit. Gravida dictum fusce ut placerat orci nulla pellentesque dignissim.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. A pellentesque sit amet porttitor. Non enim praesent elementum facilisis. Nunc aliquet bibendum enim facilisis gravida neque convallis a. Vitae aliquet nec ullamcorper sit amet risus nullam. Porttitor lacus luctus accumsan tortor posuere ac ut consequat semper. Pulvinar etiam non quam lacus suspendisse. Cursus risus at ultrices mi tempus imperdiet nulla malesuada pellentesque. Morbi enim nunc faucibus a pellentesque sit. Gravida dictum fusce ut placerat orci nulla pellentesque dignissim.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.grid</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The result is a less dreadful version of what we had above, and it’s definitely more readable now that each section has a shorter width.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/177b26a9b238a956b8b68993561f1016/03914/lorem-ipsum-columns.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.54430379746836%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Lorem Ipsum Columns\"\n        title=\"Lorem Ipsum Columns\"\n        src=\"/static/177b26a9b238a956b8b68993561f1016/f058b/lorem-ipsum-columns.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/177b26a9b238a956b8b68993561f1016/c26ae/lorem-ipsum-columns.png 158w,\n/static/177b26a9b238a956b8b68993561f1016/6bdcf/lorem-ipsum-columns.png 315w,\n/static/177b26a9b238a956b8b68993561f1016/f058b/lorem-ipsum-columns.png 630w,\n/static/177b26a9b238a956b8b68993561f1016/40601/lorem-ipsum-columns.png 945w,\n/static/177b26a9b238a956b8b68993561f1016/03914/lorem-ipsum-columns.png 1173w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Equal Spacing Between Columns and Rows</h2>\n<p>However, the columns are packed too close together, so it’s hard to tell where one section starts and another section ends.</p>\n<p>Let’s put a <code class=\"language-text\">20px</code> gap between columns and <code class=\"language-text\">10px</code> gap between rows.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.grid</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ...\n  <span class=\"token property\">column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">row-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/00d606e10e231941cef66f5e9c2c7131/19a6b/lorem-ipsum-grid-gaps.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.72151898734178%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Lorem Ipsum Grid Gaps\"\n        title=\"Lorem Ipsum Grid Gaps\"\n        src=\"/static/00d606e10e231941cef66f5e9c2c7131/f058b/lorem-ipsum-grid-gaps.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/00d606e10e231941cef66f5e9c2c7131/c26ae/lorem-ipsum-grid-gaps.png 158w,\n/static/00d606e10e231941cef66f5e9c2c7131/6bdcf/lorem-ipsum-grid-gaps.png 315w,\n/static/00d606e10e231941cef66f5e9c2c7131/f058b/lorem-ipsum-grid-gaps.png 630w,\n/static/00d606e10e231941cef66f5e9c2c7131/40601/lorem-ipsum-grid-gaps.png 945w,\n/static/00d606e10e231941cef66f5e9c2c7131/19a6b/lorem-ipsum-grid-gaps.png 1191w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>It’s starting to look better. We can clearly see where the gaps/gutters are between each row and column.</p>\n<h2>Using Media Queries to Adjust Column Amount</h2>\n<p>While we said earlier that long strings of text are not ideal on wider screens, the opposite is also true. A smaller width could also make it hard to read, especially if there are many columns.</p>\n<p>We can adjust the amount of columns to display for different device widths by using media queries. We may want 3 columns on desktop, but on tablets we can display 2 columns, and on mobile, 1 column.</p>\n<p>For simplicity, let’s consider a width of <code class=\"language-text\">900px</code> and below a tablet, and a width of <code class=\"language-text\">600px</code> and below a mobile phone.</p>\n<h3>Tablet</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.grid</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> ... <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Tablets */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> screen <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 900px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.grid</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1fr 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/61b3ded9ea0fbfc1f45fc4d5025c9721/2a50c/lorem-ipsum-tablet.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 93.0379746835443%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Lorem Ipsum Tablet\"\n        title=\"Lorem Ipsum Tablet\"\n        src=\"/static/61b3ded9ea0fbfc1f45fc4d5025c9721/f058b/lorem-ipsum-tablet.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/61b3ded9ea0fbfc1f45fc4d5025c9721/c26ae/lorem-ipsum-tablet.png 158w,\n/static/61b3ded9ea0fbfc1f45fc4d5025c9721/6bdcf/lorem-ipsum-tablet.png 315w,\n/static/61b3ded9ea0fbfc1f45fc4d5025c9721/f058b/lorem-ipsum-tablet.png 630w,\n/static/61b3ded9ea0fbfc1f45fc4d5025c9721/2a50c/lorem-ipsum-tablet.png 925w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Mobile Phone</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* Tablets */</span>\n...\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Mobile */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> screen <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 600px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.grid</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/62b7c8a5eeed0ab4db3e91e55b28d497/4597d/lorem-ipsum-phone.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 136.0759493670886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Lorem Ipsum Phone\"\n        title=\"Lorem Ipsum Phone\"\n        src=\"/static/62b7c8a5eeed0ab4db3e91e55b28d497/f058b/lorem-ipsum-phone.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/62b7c8a5eeed0ab4db3e91e55b28d497/c26ae/lorem-ipsum-phone.png 158w,\n/static/62b7c8a5eeed0ab4db3e91e55b28d497/6bdcf/lorem-ipsum-phone.png 315w,\n/static/62b7c8a5eeed0ab4db3e91e55b28d497/f058b/lorem-ipsum-phone.png 630w,\n/static/62b7c8a5eeed0ab4db3e91e55b28d497/4597d/lorem-ipsum-phone.png 631w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Adding More Elements to Grid Sections</h2>\n<p>When using a grid layout, the immediate children of the grid container (in this case the <code class=\"language-text\">div</code> with class <code class=\"language-text\">grid</code>) are the ones that get rearranged into rows and columns.</p>\n<p>Let’s encapsulate the existing paragraphs into a <code class=\"language-text\">div</code> and give each one a title as well.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. A pellentesque sit amet porttitor. Non enim praesent elementum facilisis. Nunc aliquet bibendum enim facilisis gravida neque convallis a. Vitae aliquet nec ullamcorper sit amet risus nullam. Porttitor lacus luctus accumsan tortor posuere ac ut consequat semper. Pulvinar etiam non quam lacus suspendisse. Cursus risus at ultrices mi tempus imperdiet nulla malesuada pellentesque. Morbi enim nunc faucibus a pellentesque sit. Gravida dictum fusce ut placerat orci nulla pellentesque dignissim.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  ...\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The grid’s immediate children retain their original structure.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/308114195bda1016fee77aab834a26fe/b6529/lorem-ipsum-title-elements.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Lorem Ipsum Title Elements\"\n        title=\"Lorem Ipsum Title Elements\"\n        src=\"/static/308114195bda1016fee77aab834a26fe/f058b/lorem-ipsum-title-elements.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/308114195bda1016fee77aab834a26fe/c26ae/lorem-ipsum-title-elements.png 158w,\n/static/308114195bda1016fee77aab834a26fe/6bdcf/lorem-ipsum-title-elements.png 315w,\n/static/308114195bda1016fee77aab834a26fe/f058b/lorem-ipsum-title-elements.png 630w,\n/static/308114195bda1016fee77aab834a26fe/40601/lorem-ipsum-title-elements.png 945w,\n/static/308114195bda1016fee77aab834a26fe/b6529/lorem-ipsum-title-elements.png 1049w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Nesting Grids within Grids</h2>\n<p>Why stop at one grid, when you can have many? You can have multiple grids nested inside each other, each with its own styling. It may seem complicated, but you’re basically applying the same concepts at a larger scale.</p>\n<p>Let’s rename <code class=\"language-text\">grid</code> to <code class=\"language-text\">grid-1</code> and create <code class=\"language-text\">grid-2</code>. The second grid will display its contents in a single column and have a <code class=\"language-text\">row-gap</code> of <code class=\"language-text\">5px</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\"